```

---

## Conventions

- **Markdown + wiki-links.** Every entity file has YAML frontmatter and uses `[[wiki-links]]` for references.
- **Obsidian-friendly.** Point an Obsidian vault at this folder to browse the graph visually.
- **One entity per file.** Name files after the entity (`jane-doe.md`, not `jane-doe-intro-meeting.md`).
- **Write situational memories.** Include when, why, and what it implies — not just facts.

---

## First steps

1. Open `CLAUDE.md` and read the session protocol.
2. Fill out `system/context/goals-metrics.md` with your current priorities.
3. Add your first person or company to `knowledge/` to see the graph start to form.
4. Tune `voice/brand-guidelines.md` so any content the agent generates already sounds like you.
5. Add your first risk rule to `risks.md` — usually "don't send anything to [X] without me reviewing it first".

